(
  'The View at The Palm: Tickets, Timings & Travel Tips',
  'the-view-at-the-palm-tickets-timings-travel-tips',
  'Complete guide to The View at The Palm observation deck — 240m up on The Palm Tower, Palm Jumeirah. Tickets, best time to visit, and how to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546483875-ad9014c88eba?w=900&q=80" alt="The View at The Palm observation deck Palm Jumeirah Dubai" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>The View at The Palm: Tickets, Timings &amp; Travel Tips</h2>
<p>Perched 240 metres up on The Palm Tower, The View at The Palm is the only observation deck that lets you see the full fronds of Palm Jumeirah spread beneath you, with the Dubai Marina skyline and open Arabian Gulf stretching to the horizon.</p>
<h2>Location &amp; Travel Times</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">From</th><th style="padding:10px;">Drive Time</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Airport (DXB)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~35 min</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Downtown Dubai</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~25 min</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Marina</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~10 min</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Al Maktoum Airport (DWC)</td><td style="padding:10px;text-align:center;">~30 min</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>What You''ll See From the Top</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Direction</th><th style="padding:10px;">View</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">North</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Full fan of Palm Jumeirah fronds and Atlantis The Royal</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">East</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Marina towers and JBR skyline</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">West</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Open Arabian Gulf, best for sunset</td></tr>
