<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Daily</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">9:00 AM – 10:00 PM</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Last Entry</td><td style="padding:10px;">9:15 PM</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Best Time to Visit</h2>
<div style="background:#f8fafc;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:16px 0;">
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Morning</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#22c55e;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:30%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#16a34a;">Clear Skies, Quiet</span></div>
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Midday</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#eab308;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:45%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#ca8a04;">Bright Haze</span></div>
<div><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Sunset (5:30–7 PM)</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#ef4444;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:95%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#dc2626;">Most Popular — Book Ahead</span></div>
</div>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Book the sunset slot online at least 2–3 days ahead — it sells out fastest</li><li>Combine your visit with dinner at Nasimi Beach or Atlantis nearby</li><li>Floor-to-ceiling glass — a wide-angle phone lens captures the fronds best</li><li>Visit is 45–60 minutes on average, no need to rush</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>The View at The Palm sits atop The Palm Tower at the base of Palm Jumeirah. Traffic onto the Palm can back up near sunset — a pre-booked private transfer avoids parking search time. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers fixed-price rides from the airport, Marina, and all Dubai hotels. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
  true,
  '2026-07-07 09:00:00+00'
),

(
  'Sky Views Observatory: A Complete Visitor Guide',
  'sky-views-observatory-complete-visitor-guide',
  'Complete guide to Sky Views Observatory in Downtown Dubai — the glass slide, Edge Walk, ticket prices, opening hours, and easiest way to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1521401830884-6c03c1c87ebb?w=900&q=80" alt="Sky Views Observatory Downtown Dubai skyline" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Sky Views Observatory: A Complete Visitor Guide</h2>
<p>Sky Views Observatory sits within the Address Sky View twin towers in Downtown Dubai, at around 220 metres. It is best known for two thrill add-ons found nowhere else in the city: a glass-bottomed sky floor and the outdoor Edge Walk, both with the Burj Khalifa as a backdrop.</p>
<h2>Location &amp; Drive Times</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">From</th><th style="padding:10px;">Drive Time</th><th style="padding:10px;">Metro</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Airport (DXB)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~20 min</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Red Line → Burj Khalifa/Dubai Mall</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Marina</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~25 min</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Red Line, direct</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;">Dubai Mall</td><td style="padding:10px;text-align:center;">~5 min walk</td><td style="padding:10px;">Same district</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>What''s Included</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Experience</th><th style="padding:10px;">Description</th><th style="padding:10px;">Recommended For</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Observation Deck</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">360° indoor viewing floor</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">All ages</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Glass Slide</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Transparent slide between towers, 3 storeys</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Thrill seekers, 1.1m+ height</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>Edge Walk</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Open-air ledge walk, harnessed</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Adults, extra ticket required</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
