<h2>Sky Views vs Burj Khalifa "At The Top"</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Factor</th><th style="padding:10px;">Sky Views</th><th style="padding:10px;">Burj Khalifa</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Height</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">~220m</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">452–555m</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Price From</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">AED 65</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">AED 169+</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Unique Feature</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Glass slide, Edge Walk</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">World''s tallest building view</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Crowds</td><td style="padding:10px;">Lower</td><td style="padding:10px;">Very High</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Book the Edge Walk separately and in advance — slots are limited daily</li><li>Closed-toe shoes required for the glass slide</li><li>Evening visits get the Burj Khalifa lit up in the background</li><li>A budget-friendly alternative to Burj Khalifa with a genuinely unique thrill factor</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Sky Views Observatory is inside the Address Sky View towers, a short walk from Dubai Mall and Burj Khalifa Metro Station. For a direct, comfortable ride, <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers fixed-price transfers from the airport and all Dubai hotels straight to Downtown. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
  true,
  '2026-07-07 10:00:00+00'
