(
  'Ain Dubai: Everything You Need to Know Before You Visit',
  'ain-dubai-everything-you-need-to-know',
  'Everything to know before visiting Ain Dubai, the world''s largest observation wheel on Bluewaters Island — capsules, tickets, timings, and transport.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527838832700-5059252407fa?w=900&q=80" alt="Ain Dubai giant observation wheel Bluewaters Island" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Ain Dubai: Everything You Need to Know Before You Visit</h2>
<p>Standing 250 metres tall on Bluewaters Island, Ain Dubai is the world''s largest and tallest observation wheel — more than twice the height of the London Eye. A single rotation takes around 38 minutes, giving unmatched views across the Marina, Palm Jumeirah, and the coastline.</p>
<h2>Location &amp; Drive Times</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">From</th><th style="padding:10px;">Drive Time</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Airport (DXB)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~30 min</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Downtown Dubai</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~25 min</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Dubai Marina / JBR</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;text-align:center;">~10 min walk from JBR via bridge</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Palm Jumeirah</td><td style="padding:10px;text-align:center;">~10 min</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Ain Dubai in Numbers</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Fact</th><th style="padding:10px;">Detail</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Height</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">250m — tallest in the world</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Capsules</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">48 air-conditioned cabins</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Capacity Per Capsule</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Up to 40 guests (shared) or private hire</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">Rotation Time</td><td style="padding:10px;">~38 minutes for a full loop</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2>Ticket Options</h2>
<table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin:16px 0;font-size:14px;"><thead><tr style="background:#1e3a5f;color:#fff;"><th style="padding:10px;text-align:left;">Ticket Type</th><th style="padding:10px;">Price (AED)</th><th style="padding:10px;">Notes</th></tr></thead><tbody>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Standard Shared Cabin</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>130–165</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Adult, one rotation</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Child (3–12)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>100–120</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">–</td></tr>
<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Private Cabin Hire</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>From 1,500+</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Whole capsule, celebrations</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:10px;">VIP Lounge Package</td><td style="padding:10px;"><strong>250+</strong></td><td style="padding:10px;">Priority boarding &amp; refreshments</td></tr>
</tbody></table>
<div style="background:#fefce8;border:1px solid #fde047;border-radius:12px;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;"><p style="font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;">Before You Go</p><p style="font-size:14px;">Ain Dubai has periodically paused operations for maintenance since opening. Always confirm current operating status and available slots on the official website before finalising your plans.</p></div>
<h2>Best Time to Visit</h2>
<div style="background:#f8fafc;border-radius:12px;padding:20px;margin:16px 0;">
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Late Afternoon</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#22c55e;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:35%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#16a34a;">Golden Light</span></div>
<div style="margin-bottom:8px;"><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Sunset</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#ef4444;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:90%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#dc2626;">Most Popular</span></div>
<div><span style="display:inline-block;width:140px;font-size:13px;">Night</span><div style="display:inline-block;background:#eab308;height:14px;border-radius:4px;width:50%;vertical-align:middle;"></div><span style="margin-left:8px;font-size:12px;color:#ca8a04;">Marina Lights</span></div>
</div>
<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Bluewaters Island has restaurants and Caesars Palace Dubai — easy to combine with dinner</li><li>Book sunset slots several days ahead — they sell out fastest</li><li>Cabins are air-conditioned, so comfortable even in Dubai summer</li><li>Parking on Bluewaters can be limited on weekends — a drop-off transfer avoids the hassle</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Bluewaters Island connects to JBR via a pedestrian bridge and to the mainland by a dedicated access road. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> provides fixed-price drop-offs right at the island entrance from the airport, Marina, and all Dubai hotels. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
  true,
  '2026-07-08 09:00:00+00'
),

(
  'Dubai Dolphinarium: Tickets, Timings & Visitor Guide',
