(
  'The Green Planet Dubai: Everything You Need to Know',
  'green-planet-dubai-everything-you-need-to-know',
  'Complete guide to The Green Planet Dubai — the indoor tropical rainforest at City Walk. Tickets, wildlife, opening hours, and how to get there.',
