<h2>The Green Planet Dubai: Everything You Need to Know</h2>
<p>The Green Planet is a four-storey bio-dome at City Walk recreating a tropical rainforest, home to more than 3,000 plants and animals — from sloths and flying foxes to poison dart frogs — all under one glass roof in the middle of the desert city.</p>
