(
  'Ski Dubai: Visitor Guide & Transportation Tips',
  'ski-dubai-visitor-guide-transportation-tips',
  'Complete visitor guide to Ski Dubai at Mall of the Emirates — snow slopes, penguins, ticket prices, opening hours, and how to get there.',
  '<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520175480921-4edfa2983e0f?w=900&q=80" alt="Ski Dubai indoor snow slope Mall of the Emirates" style="width:100%;border-radius:16px;margin-bottom:24px;max-height:400px;object-fit:cover;"/>
<h2>Ski Dubai: Visitor Guide &amp; Transportation Tips</h2>
<p>Ski Dubai at Mall of the Emirates was the Middle East''s first indoor ski resort, and it remains one of Dubai''s most surprising attractions — a genuine snow mountain, complete with real snowfall, kept at -1°C to -6°C year-round while it is 40°C outside.</p>
