<tr style="background:#f8fafc;"><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;">Snow Park Pass (2 hrs)</td><td style="padding:10px;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;"><strong>210–230</strong></td></tr>
