<h2>Tips</h2><ul><li>Book tickets 2–4 weeks ahead for major touring productions</li><li>Smart-casual to formal dress code depending on the show</li><li>Arrive early to enjoy the Opera Plaza and Burj Khalifa Lake views</li><li>Valet parking available, but a pre-booked drop-off avoids the search entirely</li></ul>
<h2>How to Get There</h2><p>Dubai Opera sits at the base of Burj Khalifa, next to Dubai Mall and the Opera Plaza. <strong>Airport Travel Taxis</strong> offers direct, fixed-price transfers from the airport and all Dubai hotels, timed to your show. <a href="/booking">Book your transfer</a></p>',
